comment: /**  * Set the name of the scope.  */
code: /**  * Set the name of the scope.  */ public void setScopeName(String scopeName) {     Assert.notNull(scopeName, "'scopeName' must not be null").     this.scopeName = scopeName. }

comment: /**  * Get the name of the scope.  */
code: /**  * Get the name of the scope.  */ public String getScopeName() {     return this.scopeName. }

comment: /**  * Set the proxy-mode to be applied to the scoped instance.  */
code: /**  * Set the proxy-mode to be applied to the scoped instance.  */ public void setScopedProxyMode(ScopedProxyMode scopedProxyMode) {     Assert.notNull(scopedProxyMode, "'scopedProxyMode' must not be null").     this.scopedProxyMode = scopedProxyMode. }

comment: /**  * Get the proxy-mode to be applied to the scoped instance.  */
code: /**  * Get the proxy-mode to be applied to the scoped instance.  */ public ScopedProxyMode getScopedProxyMode() {     return this.scopedProxyMode. }
